abstract: Graeme McDowell shoots eight-under-par 63 in Playa del Carmen, Mexico, to take lead after two rounds of OHL Classic.
lead_paragraph: Graeme McDowell made seven birdies in an eight-hole stretch and shot an eight-under-par 63 to take the lead after two rounds of the O.H.L. Classic in Playa del Carmen, Mexico.
